                              ቀስተተ፡[sic] መሐላሁ፡ ለኖኅ፡…</q>
                            Cp. the same text in <locus from="118rb" to="119rb">118rb-119rb</locus>
                           <note>See also the same text in <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmkl001#ms_i1.2.2"></ref></note>
